# VisionTrackAI

VisionTrackAI is an advanced computer vision project designed to detect, analyze, and track objects in real-time using artificial intelligence.

## Overview
This project combines machine learning, deep learning, and image processing technologies to create smart visual monitoring systems for various industries.

## Core Features
- Real-time object recognition
- Intelligent motion tracking
- Video stream analysis
- Automated monitoring
- Performance optimization

## Applications
- Smart surveillance
- Traffic management
- Healthcare monitoring
- Industrial automation
- Security systems

## Tech Stack
- Python
- OpenCV
- TensorFlow / PyTorch
- NumPy
- Machine Learning Algorithms

## Objective
To develop a scalable AI-powered vision system that improves efficiency, security, and automation through accurate visual intelligence.

## Future Enhancements
- Facial recognition integration
- Cloud deployment
- IoT connectivity
